1
00:00:11,320 --> 00:00:22,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="TimesNewRoman"><font size="36"><font color="#4cb7b8">{\an7}Wash <font color="#2e1a12">It</font></font></font></font></font>

2
00:00:12,300 --> 00:00:22,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="TimesNewRoman"><font size="36">{\an7}<font color="#2e1a12">All Away</font></font></font></font>

3
00:01:31,780 --> 00:01:36,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="13"><font color="#042c22"><font face="Times New Roman">Episode<font color="#c76580"> 12        <font color="#439fa4">Local Cleaning <font color="#010202">with a Heart</font></font></font></font></font></font></font>

4
00:01:45,590 --> 00:01:49,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, may I ask you to take care of this?</font>

5
00:01:49,270 --> 00:01:51,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

6
00:01:51,010 --> 00:01:55,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much. 
Please allow me to inspect the garment.</font>

7
00:01:55,870 --> 00:01:59,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two sure are dressed up today. 
Are you going somewhere together?</font>

8
00:01:59,580 --> 00:02:01,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, to Izu.</font>

9
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:05,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To stay the night! 
I'm going to take a bunch of pictures</font>

10
00:02:05,020 --> 00:02:09,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and draw sketches of capybaras, 
crocodiles, and bananas!</font>

11
00:02:09,290 --> 00:02:12,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Do those things go together?</font>

12
00:02:12,110 --> 00:02:16,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll bring you back a souvenir, 
so please expect something nice!</font>

13
00:02:16,010 --> 00:02:16,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

14
00:02:21,070 --> 00:02:26,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A trip sounds nice. I'd love to go 
somewhere far away for a change.</font>

15
00:02:26,170 --> 00:02:28,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you plotting to skip town, then?</font>

16
00:02:28,920 --> 00:02:30,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah! Aji-san?</font>

17
00:02:30,700 --> 00:02:32,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, just kidding.</font>

18
00:02:35,470 --> 00:02:36,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here.</font>

19
00:02:37,050 --> 00:02:38,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care of these.</font>

20
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:43,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much. Allow me to 
inspect your items at the counter.</font>

21
00:02:43,310 --> 00:02:46,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Again? It's the same stuff as always.</font>

22
00:02:46,860 --> 00:02:50,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need to check every 
single time. For crying out loud.</font>

23
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:54,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I must! No matter how carefully 
you handle your clothes,</font>

24
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:59,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they may become worn or discolored, 
or stretch or shrink over time.</font>

25
00:02:59,050 --> 00:03:04,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Buttons and seams can unravel, and you 
might have stains that aren't easy to see.</font>

26
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:07,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is why I must check 
every single time!</font>

27
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:09,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh.</font>

28
00:03:09,110 --> 00:03:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'm sorry.</font>

29
00:03:11,330 --> 00:03:13,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't mean to come across as pushy.</font>

30
00:03:14,250 --> 00:03:17,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine, then. Do it your way.</font>

31
00:03:21,970 --> 00:03:29,860
<font size="8" color="#4c4646">Orders will be ready
<font color="#4c4646"><font face="Arial">on the <font color="#e39d9c"><b><font size="24">26th</font></b></font></font></font></font>

32
00:03:23,030 --> 00:03:26,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How long has it been since 
you set up here. Two years?</font>

33
00:03:26,620 --> 00:03:27,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

34
00:03:28,180 --> 00:03:29,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right, right.</font>

35
00:03:30,650 --> 00:03:34,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you're still using 
the same old ironing table.</font>

36
00:03:34,820 --> 00:03:39,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I am. I try to take good care of 
the equipment passed down to me.</font>

37
00:03:39,740 --> 00:03:42,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad you're able to 
make use of such an antique.</font>

38
00:03:42,890 --> 00:03:46,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all because you maintained 
everything, Aji-san.</font>

39
00:03:46,430 --> 00:03:50,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't maintain a thing. 
I just left it all alone.</font>

40
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:56,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's taking so long?</font>

41
00:03:56,260 --> 00:04:02,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, Aji-san, excuse me, but would you 
mind if I asked you something?</font>

42
00:04:02,300 --> 00:04:05,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What now? Is it about the rent?</font>

43
00:04:15,030 --> 00:04:19,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine, then. If it's that much of a hassle,
 I'll just wash it myself.</font>

44
00:04:19,030 --> 00:04:21,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, that's not what I meant.</font>

45
00:04:23,550 --> 00:04:25,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I simply wanted to...</font>

46
00:04:35,430 --> 00:04:36,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

47
00:04:36,010 --> 00:04:40,010
<font size="8" color="#4c4646">Orders will be ready
<font color="#4c4646"><font face="Arial">on the <font color="#cc7571"><b><font size="24">8th</font></b></font></font></font></font>

48
00:04:36,450 --> 00:04:38,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And he ran off without saying a word?</font>

49
00:04:38,970 --> 00:04:40,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

50
00:04:45,050 --> 00:04:48,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What? Kyusho-kun?</font>

51
00:04:48,930 --> 00:04:53,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if I did something 
to make him uncomfortable.</font>

52
00:04:53,440 --> 00:04:56,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course not. Don't even worry about it.</font>

53
00:04:56,380 --> 00:04:58,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure he was just embarrassed.</font>

54
00:04:58,290 --> 00:04:59,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Embarrassed?</font>

55
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:00,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, sure.</font>

56
00:05:00,710 --> 00:05:03,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're talking about a boy who's still 
making his way through puberty, right?</font>

57
00:05:03,950 --> 00:05:06,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, come on, Kinme-san!</font>

58
00:05:06,060 --> 00:05:08,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if you're right.</font>

59
00:05:08,700 --> 00:05:11,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am. So you don't need to worry.</font>

60
00:05:19,470 --> 00:05:21,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font face="Arial"><font color="#473e3a">Kinme</font></font></b></font>

61
00:05:30,980 --> 00:05:33,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font color="#525155"><font size="24">Timer</font></font></b></font>

62
00:05:30,980 --> 00:05:31,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font color="#525155"><font size="30">Start</font></font></b></font>

63
00:05:30,980 --> 00:05:31,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font color="#525155"><font size="30">Pause</font></font></b></font>

64
00:05:37,270 --> 00:05:39,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Verdana"><font color="#68655e"><font size="26">We are closed for the day.</font></font></font></font>

65
00:05:47,790 --> 00:05:50,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="TimesNewRoman">{\an8}<font color="#655f57">September Rent</font></font></font>

66
00:05:47,790 --> 00:05:50,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="TimesNewRoman">{\an8}<font color="#655f57"><font size="12">Kinme Wakana
Kinme Cleaning</font></font></font></font>

67
00:05:51,270 --> 00:05:54,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She usually comes to pick it up 
at the end of the month.</i></font>

68
00:05:54,920 --> 00:06:01,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, Aji-san, excuse me but would you 
mind if I asked you something?</font>

69
00:06:01,140 --> 00:06:03,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What now? Is it about the rent?</font>

70
00:06:03,930 --> 00:06:08,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, Aji-san, how have you 
been feeling recently?</font>

71
00:06:08,930 --> 00:06:11,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What are you talking about?</font>

72
00:06:11,450 --> 00:06:16,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know what I say. 
I've always been healthy as a horse.</font>

73
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:17,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmph!</font>

74
00:06:18,290 --> 00:06:23,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I noticed something similar the last time 
you brought your laundry in,</font>

75
00:06:23,100 --> 00:06:28,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but there appears to be a stain 
in the crotch area I hadn't seen before.</font>

76
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:29,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could this mean...</font>

77
00:06:32,950 --> 00:06:37,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ffffff">Fine, then. If it's that much of a hassle,
 I'll just wash it myself.</font></font>

78
00:06:40,460 --> 00:06:43,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I must have offended her.</i></font>

79
00:06:44,230 --> 00:06:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What do I do now?</i></font>

80
00:06:47,470 --> 00:06:49,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="TimesNewRoman">{\an8}<font color="#655f57">September Rent</font></font></font>

81
00:06:47,470 --> 00:06:49,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="TimesNewRoman">{\an8}<font color="#655f57"><font size="12">Kinme Wakana
Kinme Cleaning</font></font></font></font>

82
00:06:53,730 --> 00:06:57,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Verdana"><font color="#5b6270"><font size="27">{\an8}Away for a moment.
Be back soon. - Manager</font></font></font></font>

83
00:07:07,830 --> 00:07:11,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So this is Aji-san's house.</i></font>

84
00:07:09,490 --> 00:07:12,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font color="#141921"><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Absolutely NO Solicitors
 Door-to-Door Sales Prohibited</b></font></font></font>

85
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:19,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I know she always says she doesn't 
want me showing up at her house.</i></font>

86
00:07:32,390 --> 00:07:35,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me, please. It's me, Kinme Wakana.</font>

87
00:07:35,610 --> 00:07:37,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you home, Aji-san?</font>

88
00:07:39,630 --> 00:07:41,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wonder if she's out.</i></font>

89
00:07:44,780 --> 00:07:46,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's open?</font>

90
00:07:50,070 --> 00:07:52,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me, please.</font>

91
00:07:52,060 --> 00:07:53,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's me, Kinme Wakana.</font>

92
00:07:56,070 --> 00:07:57,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Aji-san!</font>

93
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:01,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry to catch you 
while you're cleaning.</font>

94
00:08:01,740 --> 00:08:05,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I went ahead and 
brought this month's rent.</font>

95
00:08:19,980 --> 00:08:24,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="22"><font color="#80c4c4">{\an7}Wash It All Away</font></font></font></font>

96
00:08:24,940 --> 00:08:29,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="22"><font color="#80c4c4">{\an7}Wash It All Away</font></font></font></font>

97
00:08:28,450 --> 00:08:31,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font color="#377f4e"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="12">We pick up and deliver!
 <font color="#3d432a"><font face="Arial"><b>Kinme Cleaning</b></font></font></font></font></font></font>

98
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:39,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, move along now.</font>

99
00:08:39,810 --> 00:08:43,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How am I gonna get 
any sweeping done? Sheesh.</font>

100
00:08:43,940 --> 00:08:47,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess all these leaves 
mean it's finally fall.</font>

101
00:08:47,710 --> 00:08:51,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I suppose it is 
that time of the year.</font>

102
00:08:51,020 --> 00:08:53,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Getting out of the house 
is gonna be a pain now.</font>

103
00:08:53,950 --> 00:08:55,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boy oh boy.</font>

104
00:08:55,890 --> 00:09:00,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I brought your clean garments for you.</font>

105
00:09:00,050 --> 00:09:01,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Appreciate it.</font>

106
00:09:01,770 --> 00:09:04,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was able to get 
the stains out completely.</font>

107
00:09:04,910 --> 00:09:08,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were you now? Thank you.</font>

108
00:09:12,070 --> 00:09:15,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, that sure was embarrassing.</font>

109
00:09:15,380 --> 00:09:19,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All the while, I kept saying, 
"I'm healthy as a horse!"</font>

110
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:24,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you read me like a book and 
knew what was wrong, didn't you?</font>

111
00:09:24,520 --> 00:09:27,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I wouldn't put it that way.</font>

112
00:09:27,910 --> 00:09:35,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am very sorry for upsetting you, though.
 I should not have spoken so carelessly.</font>

113
00:09:36,930 --> 00:09:43,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all right. If you hadn't been worried
 about me, I might not have made it.</font>

114
00:09:47,020 --> 00:09:51,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I felt myself starting to pass out, 
I thought that was it for me.</font>

115
00:09:52,150 --> 00:09:57,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should've listened to your warning 
and gotten checked at the hospital</font>

116
00:09:57,350 --> 00:10:00,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">instead of ignoring it 
until I ended up collapsing.</font>

117
00:10:00,040 --> 00:10:06,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't call it a warning. I wasn't 
aware of your condition, after all.</font>

118
00:10:07,630 --> 00:10:13,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just, the longer I get to know my 
customers as their neighborhood cleaner,</font>

119
00:10:13,460 --> 00:10:18,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do start to notice when there are 
slight changes in their garments.</font>

120
00:10:19,830 --> 00:10:23,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'll think, "Oh, it looks like 
her weight changed a little"</font>

121
00:10:23,580 --> 00:10:27,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or "He must have gone through something 
that made him sweat a lot."</font>

122
00:10:28,500 --> 00:10:33,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really only wanted to share 
with you what I had noticed.</font>

123
00:10:35,090 --> 00:10:38,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're like a criminal profiler, 
in a manner of speaking.</font>

124
00:10:38,700 --> 00:10:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pro-what?</font>

125
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:43,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I just mean to say</font>

126
00:10:43,580 --> 00:10:48,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that people who work as cleaners 
actually have a pretty important job.</font>

127
00:10:50,570 --> 00:10:51,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I agree!</font>

128
00:10:52,100 --> 00:10:56,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Speaking of which, your shop is 
two years old now, isn't it?</font>

129
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:58,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, yes! I couldn't have 
made it without you.</font>

130
00:10:58,850 --> 00:11:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh boy, I remember how 
stressful things were at first</font>

131
00:11:02,900 --> 00:11:05,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when you didn't have many customers.</font>

132
00:11:05,330 --> 00:11:10,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was so afraid that you might not 
make rent, it gave me the chills.</font>

133
00:11:11,350 --> 00:11:13,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I remember that.</font>

134
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:18,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I was soon able to build a regular 
customer base thanks to your advice.</font>

135
00:11:19,190 --> 00:11:22,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You told me that because of all 
the hills and stairs in this town,</font>

136
00:11:22,170 --> 00:11:25,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there are elderly folks who can't get 
to my shop even if they want to.</font>

137
00:11:26,390 --> 00:11:28,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And with all of the winding, narrow roads,</font>

138
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:32,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it can be tough getting 
around even in a car.</font>

139
00:11:33,130 --> 00:11:35,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I heard that, I thought, "Okay,</font>

140
00:11:35,860 --> 00:11:39,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to think of a way to serve 
this community's needs."</font>

141
00:11:40,510 --> 00:11:41,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why...</font>

142
00:11:47,790 --> 00:11:53,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I decided the shop motto should be 
"Local Cleaning with a Heart."</font>

143
00:12:00,860 --> 00:12:02,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seems fitting.</font>

144
00:12:02,450 --> 00:12:07,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, are you planning anything special 
for your second anniversary?</font>

145
00:12:07,160 --> 00:12:09,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yes!</font>

146
00:12:09,090 --> 00:12:12,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was thinking of throwing a special 
second anniversary event</font>

147
00:12:12,030 --> 00:12:14,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to show my appreciation 
to all of my customers.</font>

148
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:17,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. Sounds nice.</font>

149
00:12:19,470 --> 00:12:21,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well then, I'll be going.</font>

150
00:12:21,430 --> 00:12:25,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When it's too much trouble to leave 
the house, I'll give you another call.</font>

151
00:12:25,490 --> 00:12:28,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure! Whenever you need me.</font>

152
00:12:30,700 --> 00:12:33,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aji-san, what's the matter?</font>

153
00:12:33,700 --> 00:12:38,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never expected that it 
would be my turn next.</font>

154
00:12:38,160 --> 00:12:39,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your turn next?</font>

155
00:12:39,820 --> 00:12:45,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I remembered I'd heard about 
something like this in the past</font>

156
00:12:45,540 --> 00:12:49,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">from the cleaning shop 
that was in there before you.</font>

157
00:12:49,780 --> 00:12:50,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

158
00:12:51,140 --> 00:12:56,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The manager then also noticed 
a change in a customer's clothes</font>

159
00:12:56,100 --> 00:12:58,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that meant their disease was progressing.</font>

