00:21:37,300 --> 00:21:40,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You shouldn't be ashamed to accept it.</font>

323
00:21:41,920 --> 00:21:42,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

324
00:21:43,500 --> 00:21:47,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that reminds me. 
Would you wait right there a minute?</font>

325
00:21:47,580 --> 00:21:48,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh...</font>

326
00:21:50,620 --> 00:21:53,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here. This one is from me.</font>

327
00:21:53,740 --> 00:21:56,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't need it, 
you can toss it for all I care.</font>

328
00:22:00,870 --> 00:22:03,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so much!</font>

329
00:22:12,860 --> 00:22:17,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It has already been two years 
since I started my shop in this city.</i></font>

330
00:22:18,530 --> 00:22:23,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When I was just starting out, 
I didn't have many regular customers,</i></font>

331
00:22:24,110 --> 00:22:28,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and there were times 
when I was unsure of the future.</i></font>

332
00:22:28,330 --> 00:22:31,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But over time, people got to 
know me and my business better,</i></font>

333
00:22:32,590 --> 00:22:36,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and as a result, 
I've been able to make it this far.</i></font>

334
00:22:44,470 --> 00:22:47,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll keep striving to live up 
to my motto to provide</i></font>

335
00:22:47,210 --> 00:22:50,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"Local Cleaning with a Heart."</i></font>

336
00:22:54,530 --> 00:22:58,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome. I'll get the door right away.</font>

337
00:22:58,100 --> 00:22:59,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

338
00:23:00,090 --> 00:23:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this your first time coming here?</font>

339
00:23:02,900 --> 00:23:07,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. Someone in the neighborhood 
recommended you.</font>

340
00:23:07,830 --> 00:23:12,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I this got dirty when 
I was out with friends yesterday.</font>

341
00:23:12,950 --> 00:23:15,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

342
00:23:15,020 --> 00:23:17,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please allow me to inspect your item.</font>

343
00:23:17,630 --> 00:23:18,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

344
00:23:21,260 --> 00:23:24,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a favorite that 
my mother bought for me.</font>

345
00:23:24,990 --> 00:23:27,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think you can clean it?</font>

346
00:23:30,920 --> 00:23:33,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can count on Kinme.</font>

347
00:23:34,890 --> 00:23:39,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><font color="#0b0a0b"><font face="Times New Roman">Thank you for <font color="#39b5b9">watching.</font></font></font></font></font>

